{"id":40188,"type":2,"name":"Mulan","name_cn":"花木兰","date":"1998-06-19","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/f4/9d/40188_P423c.jpg","rating":{"rank":2679,"total":665,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":2,"4":8,"5":40,"6":133,"7":304,"8":147,"9":21,"10":9},"score":6.9},"summary":"花木兰是家中的长女，性格爽朗率真，父母极力想帮女儿找到一个好归宿，可是多次努力未果。此时却收到了北方匈奴侵略的消息，朝廷召集各家各户的壮丁。木兰父亲也在名单之内，木兰不忍年迈残疾的父亲征战沙场，决定割掉长发，偷走父亲的盔甲，决定女扮男装代父从军。花家的祖先为了保护木兰，便派出了心地善良的木须从旁帮忙。从军的过程中，木兰凭着坚强意志，通过了一关又一关的艰苦训练，她的精神也感动了所有战友。就在战况告急的时候，她也被发现了女子的身份。她被遗留在雪地中，而最后也是她的及时出现，顺利协助大军击退了匈奴。\r\n\r\n简介来自豆瓣（https://movie.douban.com/subject/1294833/）。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>花木兰</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>脚本: </span>Rita Hsiao、Christopher Sanders、<a href=\"/person/52910\">Philip LaZebnik</a>、Raymond Singer、Eugenia Bostwick-Singer</li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/34842\">Jerry Goldsmith</a></li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span><a href=\"/person/17184\">成龍</a></li><li><span>製作: </span><a href=\"/person/6816\">Walt Disney Pictures</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/13956\">Walt Disney Animation Studios</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>China Doll</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>The Legend of Mulan</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>木兰</li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1998年6月19日</li><li><span>片长: </span>88分钟</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.mulan.com/</li><li><span>导演: </span>Tony Bancroft、Barry Cook</li><li><span>原作: </span>Robert D. San Souci</li><li><span>原案: </span>John Sanford、Chris Williams、Tim Hodge、Julius Aguimatang、Burny Mattinson、Lorna Cook、Barry Johnson、Thom Enriquez、Ed Gombert、Joe Grant、Floyd Norman</li><li><span>制片人: </span>Pam Coats</li>","collection":{"on_hold":11,"dropped":8,"wish":26,"collect":1199,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"迪士尼","count":190},{"name":"欧美","count":157},{"name":"剧场版","count":126},{"name":"童年","count":119},{"name":"1998","count":89},{"name":"Disney","count":75},{"name":"动画电影","count":59},{"name":"美国","count":38},{"name":"中国元素","count":38},{"name"